headline: Elon Musk, Jensen Huang, and the other billionaires who made bank in 2024
summary: 2024 was a major year for the world’s wealthiest Americans as the stock market continued to notch new highs. The S&P 500 hit more than 50 record highs over the past 12 months, with its first occurring as early as Jan. 19.
